1. Open the Discord Developer Portal (dashboard) for your bot.
2. Go to the "Bot" tab.
3. Click on the "Reset Secret" button.
4. Click on the "Copy" button to copy the new token.
5. Replace `YOUR_BOT_TOKEN_HERE` with the new token.

This bot will ban a user when the `/ban` command is used, specifying the user and an optional reason. The bot requires the `BAN_MEMBERS` permission.

Make sure to reinstall your bot on your server and restart it before using the `/ban` command.

